<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 Na-za-reth Jesuh hmaiah cun khuaruahhar ngai in ka dir, Sual thurmi
 kei hmanh a ka dawt, Khuaruahhar ngai ngai a si.

[C1]
   Zei tluk khuaruahhar Khuaruahhar tiin ka sak zungzal lai. Zeitluk
   khuaruahhar, Khuaruahhar, Khamhtu a ka dawtnak cu!

[V2]
 &quot;Na duhnak bang siseh,&quot; ti'n kei ruangah dum ah thla a cam, Amah ca a
 tah a si lo, Kei ca thlan thi dor a tla.

[C2]
   Zei tluk khuaruahhar Khuaruahhar tiin ka sak zungzal lai. Zeitluk
   khuaruahhar, Khuaruahhar, Khamhtu a ka dawtnak cu!

[V3]
 Ka sual ngaihchiatnak a kalpi, Amah theng te nih aa phorh, Kalvary lei
 panh in a kal, Temh-innak he a thi cang.

[C3]
   Zei tluk khuaruahhar Khuaruahhar tiin ka sak zungzal lai. Zeitluk
   khuaruahhar, Khuaruahhar, Khamhtu a ka dawtnak cu!

[V4]
 Tlanh ciami hna he sunparnak in, A hmai ka hmuh tikah, Dong loin kaa
 lawmh laimi cu, A dawtnak kong sak a si.

[C4]
   Zei tluk khuaruahhar Khuaruahhar tiin ka sak zungzal lai. Zeitluk
   khuaruahhar, Khuaruahhar, Khamhtu a ka dawtnak cu!</lyrics>
<key>Ab</key>
<title>KA KHAMHTU DAWTNAK CH17</title>
<hymn_number>17</hymn_number>
</song>